ISLAMABAD, Sep 04 (APP): The Election Commission of Pakistan (ECP) has decided to hold in abeyance, the Election Progarmme issued vide its notification of even dated August 20, 2024 for the conduct of local government elections in Islamabad Capital Territory, till further orders.
The ECP held in abeyance the local government elections in ICT in consequent upon the recent amendments made by the Parliament in the Islamabad Capital Territory Local Government Act, 2015 through the Islamabad Capital Territory Local Government (Amendment) Act, 2024 dated 30th August, 2024, said a notification issued on Wednesday.
